{"tid":387957,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[四腳動物]廣州興起龜蛇爬行鍛鍊肌肉治頸脊病","createTime":"2017-09-05T05:33:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-07T10:00:45.000Z","uid":34409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fe61e085b6f53e99fdb9ff9da554b114f456511e","tid":387957,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T05:33:20.000Z","msg":"【鍛鍊肌肉治頸脊病】<br />\n【龜蛇爬行廣州興起】<br />\n<br />\n果真是「高手在民間」？<br />\n<br />\n廣州一個公園有位高人，推廣一種獨特的強身健體的方法，精髓是學龜搖頭擺腦，學蛇扭動腰骨，是為「龜蛇爬行」運動。<br />\n<br />\n推廣人李培良 30 年前因為自身的頸腰椎問題，創出這種運動，今年 87 歲的李培良，體格健壯，身手靈活。他表示，爬行對預防心腦血管病，非常有效。<br />\n<br />\n有中醫師指出，龜蛇爬行動作其實藏有許多細節，能夠鍛鍊全身肌肉。<br />\n<br />\n「由下肢開始發力，用雙腳撐地，然後他的力量會傳到骨盤，接著帶動整個脊椎。」<br />\n<br />\n「脊椎不是固定的，而是自然扭轉的動作，然後到頭部、肩部，由軀幹帶動四肢。」<br />\n<br />\n不過醫師認為，龜蛇爬行運動量大，而且需要一定技巧，才可達到保健功效。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/729548727237198/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ficablenews%2Fvideos%2F729548727237198%2F&d=eD48OVMchSvo1iK61qzxjoS5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=0c7dba99\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/729548727237198/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://z9x9.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/08/25/20170825_59a00b43cbb7f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fz9x9.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F08%2F25%2F20170825_59a00b43cbb7f.jpg&h=7e6781a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://proc.iifs.ifeng.com/blog/2016/04/17/l6KhypeTmKuoa3OnvNd2fL2anGmRl2CMyqqPomVrb5Ftb2OZaGqQwm2XZ5aX3mRmlJLCZJWPYZLBo6eX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fproc.iifs.ifeng.com%2Fblog%2F2016%2F04%2F17%2Fl6KhypeTmKuoa3OnvNd2fL2anGmRl2CMyqqPomVrb5Ftb2OZaGqQwm2XZ5aX3mRmlJLCZJWPYZLBo6eX.jpg&h=55d6eb56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://is1.mzstatic.com/image/thumb/Purple7/v4/74/d5/cb/74d5cbf3-5d30-14e2-63c8-4fd81468698a/source/512x512bb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fis1.mzsta